&lt;h3&gt;Green Ridge Complex Trail Closure&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident:&lt;/strong&gt; Green Ridge Complex Wildfire&lt;br/&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Released:&lt;/strong&gt; 32 min. ago&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;BITTERROOT NATIONAL FOREST&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;1801 N. First Street&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Hamilton, MT 59840&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Forest Supervisor's Order&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p align="center" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-align: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;EMERGENCY FIRE CLOSURE – Green Ridge Complex Fire&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Pursuant to Title 36 Code of Federal Regulations 261.50(b), the following act is prohibited as described below within the West Fork Ranger District of the Bitterroot National Forest. These restrictions are in addition to those enumerated in Subpart A, Part 261, Title 36, Code of Federal Regulations, and become effective upon signing and will remain in effect until rescinded. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;The purpose of this order is to protect the public from potential harm from wildfires and firefighting operations associated with the Green Ridge Complex Fire. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;36 CFR 261.53 – Special Closures:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;It is prohibited to enter or be upon any area which is closed for the protection of “Public Health and Safety”: &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;(Title 36 CFR 261.53(e)).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;36 CFR 261.55 – National Forest System Trails:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; All persons are prohibited from being on any National Forest System Trail as described below:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; (Title 36 CFR 261.55(a))&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: .8in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; tab-stops: .8in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;The trail closure description follows with a map attachment Description of Trails:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Within the Selway-Bitterroot Wilderness&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; NFST #40, West of the intersection of NFST # 40 &amp;amp; 4 &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-indent: 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;NFST #3, West of Pack Bridge south of Indian Creek Campground&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; text-indent: 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;NFST #536, East of the boundary of the Bitterroot National Forest and Nez Perce – Clearwater National Forest&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Exemptions:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Pursuant to 36 CFR 261.50(e), the following are exempt from this order:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; tab-stops: list .75in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;1.&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Persons with a permit issued by a forest officer specifically authorizing the otherwise prohibited act or omission.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.5in; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;2.&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Any Federal, State, or local officer, or member of an organized rescue or firefighting force in the performance of an official duty.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="text-indent: -0.25in; margin-left: 0.5in; tab-stops: list .5in; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;3.&lt;/font&gt; &lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Persons engaged in business, trade, or occupation in the area.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin-left: 0.5in;"&gt;&lt;font face="Times New Roman"&gt;Signed in Hamilton, Montana, this &lt;u&gt;5th &lt;/u&gt; day of September, 2017.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 