"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0.1in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Bitterroot National Forest&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Penalty&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 3.25in;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Violation of these prohibitions is punishable by a fine of not more than $5,000 for an individual or $10,000 for an organization, or imprisonment for not more than six (6) months, or both (16 USC 551 and 18 USC 3559 and 3571).&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan;"&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;Notification&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman" size="3"&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; tab-stops: 3.25in;"&gt;&lt;font color="#000000"&gt;A copy of this orde